
This is an educational game for kids that intends to be a fun way to learn geography becoming in Aladdin, Iago or Genie. The kids have to situate the name of the country in the map, It also has some cool information about the country which will get them closer to the culture of that country. The kids can choose between a trainning mode where they can improve their knowledge about a specific continent or a normal mode where the challenge is go throught all of them. 

Use your mouse and click on the map
